 156424B. Using\nH$\\alpha$, as well as other variable spectral lines, we determine a period of\nabout 0.52 d, making HD 156424B one of the most rapidly rotating magnetic hot\nstars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 19:03:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-07"}
