 relaxation. The long relaxation\nis consistent with the vanishing density of states in Dirac spectrum and slow\nspin-repolarization of the SOC-controlled band structure accompanying the\nemergence of Dirac fermions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 2020 22:33:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-06"}
